|IP_{AB}| = 2 d_{AB} \sin\frac{\alpha_2}{2}\sin\frac{\pi_2+\beta_2-\alpha_2}{2} = \frac{4d\sin\alpha_4 \sin\beta_2\sin\gamma_2\sin(\pi_4+\beta_4-\alpha_4)}{\cos(\beta_2-\alpha_2)}
